{"tid":804450,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"約咗條女中秋前食飯，但…","createTime":"2018-09-03T04:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T14:16:44.000Z","uid":164158,"like":43,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9df412188273e9fa862f5387cc763f98bda428fd","tid":804450,"uid":164158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:34:31.000Z","msg":"是咁的，話說同佢喺大學度識，一開始個陣因為喺設計課，女都比較多，冇點留意佢，佢小肥 面圓 偽abc 感覺。<br />\n佢就經常坐我隔離（明明好多位）又特登等埋一齊食飯，不時message 到好夜。<br />\n<br />\n感覺到佢喺想同我一齊，但個陣因為屋企問題，又想專心學業，所以冇回應到佢唧心意，開始冷淡疏遠，可能feel到冇意思，大家漸漸就冇聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n直到最近，大家喺D舊同學聚會遇到，又開始聯絡返，傾下D近況，<br />\n而我自己就dry咗一段時間，咪膽粗粗約佢出黎食飯，都驚之前唧冷淡佢會拒絕我，點知又應承咗出黎喺中秋前食飯。<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得我應該 ：<br />\n食咗先睇下有冇得發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定 唔喺真心就唔好搞人喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff3697ba9bbcf24bdb857ec7bfc7a245b8e6e02","tid":804450,"uid":71433,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:35:59.000Z","msg":"食完就中出"},{"pid":"24b0c806acfcb055ee9db825b426af2766fbfd1f","tid":804450,"uid":67908,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:36:52.000Z","msg":"啱，食咗先，再睇下有冇得發展"},{"pid":"60363a55604fbcbdefc70cfa3543274c96a4f065","tid":804450,"uid":151412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:37:09.000Z","msg":"食完睇下點先算啦 飯都未食 唸咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6e4e4bf07a12cad5ffdfe0ea761ecda2128aa0","tid":804450,"uid":206253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:37:18.000Z","msg":"有食唔食 罪大惡極"},{"pid":"758db8e2f1723ce9c19ff30e705d4424fe1229a0","tid":804450,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:54:54.000Z","msg":"不要暗戀"},{"pid":"fdbbb4c320006d55c31bd9b2cc1ba4a8e604b8c8","tid":804450,"uid":198280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:00:47.000Z","msg":"食飯我就唔知喇，中出就緊既"},{"pid":"6748df03